summary: hi love ! i was wondering if you could make a post on how bangtan would comfort you? like when you’re upset and sad, ty !!
question: hi love ! i was wondering if you could make a post on how bangtan would comfort you? like when you’re upset and sad, ty !!
answer:
I’m on mobile so the format might be OFF 🗿 but here goes !

Namjoon

I think namjoon would be the best person to go to for comfort. His libra mercury would know just the right words to say to make you feel better. With his sag moon, he’d love to cheer you up !!! His scorpio venus, I think, if you’re his partner, would shower you with attention and love.

Seokjin

Jin would crack puns all the time. His sag sun & aries moon just wants to make you laugh, either at his jokes or at him. He’d make faces (such an aries moon thing), like he’s not afraid to embarrass himself if it meant for u to smile again !! A true sag 20/10

Yoongi

I think Yoongi will be “subtle” about it. Like how in the Burn the Stage ep he’d be like “well I think your voice is nice. I like ur voice best” to Jimin. He’s not the type like jin who goes out of his way to make u laugh, his pisces sun/merc would be v empathetic. He’d feel for you, and try to understand you, so his words of comfort can rly hit home

Hoseok

Hobi has a pisces merc as well, so very much like Yoongi. He’d be empathetic, but at the same time bc of his Taurus moon & aqua sun, he’d be like 🗿🗿 uhhh air & earth signs have a hard time expressing their feelings, so while he might seem aloof, he actually does care a lot ! He’d make u forget about ur problems !!

Jimin

Oof, another libra mercury in the works !! He’d know just what to say to you to make u feel better, plus his Scorpio venus is just like namjoon too. He’s that gordon Ramsay meme where he’s like I’m not leaving until I see u smile

Taehyung

Tae might not be the best at comforting due to his cold & reserves cap sun/merc & aloof aqua venus. He, like jin, has an aries moon, so I think he’d try to make u feel better by trying to make u laugh w his expressive aries moon !!

JungKook

Jungkook’s Virgo mercury means well lmao but they’re so awkward 🗿🗿 he’d feel bad and wants to cheer u up but he’d be like uhHhHh WHATS HaPp his leo moon tho? Shower u w compliments like “wym ur so good at this” “I think it looked perfect” “ur so creative I love ur works” “that friend doesn’t deserve u” etc etc !!
